                      WESTWOOD GLOBAL INVESTMENTS, LLC
                    

•   BOSTON, MA
                          • Investment Advisor
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Westwood Global Investments is based out of Boston. Westwood Global Investments is a large advisory firm with  11-25 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $8,919,279,019 (Form ADV from 2017-03-31).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $1,154,101,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 99.33%. Westwood Global Investments's largest holding is Itau Unibnco ADR with shares held of 27,422,576.  Westwood Global Investments has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 48 13F filings in our database for Westwood Global Investments. 
                                           






